lead_paragraph: Two goals from Eden Hazard inspired Chelsea to a ruthless 5-0 rout of Everton on Saturday that sent Antonio Conte's resurgent Blues to the top of the Premier League table.

headline.print_headline: Five-Star Chelsea Destroy Everton to Go Top
